Greatly reduces the accuracy and bullet speed of the Ogre in favor of around 25% increased fire rate, 10% damage and no spinup time to make it act similarly to the bl3 ogre. 
 Bullet speed is comparable to the harold at close range (slightly faster). Each bullet fired from a non-slippery version displays obvious rocket trails and smoke.
 Using a slippery version helps with the speed penalty and makes it more versatile overall.
 The ogre becomes a beast at close range (on axton or krieg) but hitting mid range crits or moving targets is much harder. 
 
 
   set GD_Aster_Weapons.FiringModes.Bullet_Assault_Ogre Speed 220.000000
 
 
